ed="T" n="0860a13"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0860a13"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="begd1e41378"/>宋<anchor xml:id="endd1e41378"/></date><placeName key="PL000000014699"><placeName>天台山</placeName><placeName>般若寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013524">師蘊</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0860a14"/><persName key="A013524">釋師蘊</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000013514">金華</placeName>人也。厥性真率，不好封植<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1943"/>，遇<lb
ed="T" n="0860a15"/>事屬情，有多訐直<ptr type="glossary" target="#g895"/>。<placeName key="PL000000048181">梁</placeName><date key="j20576132058505" notAfter-iso="+0923-11-23" notBefore-iso="+0921-06-14"><name>龍德</name>中</date>，與<persName key="A008355">德韶<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0860a16"/>結侶遐征，遊訪名師勝境。至於北<placeName key="PL000000005250"><placeName>代</placeName><placeName>清涼<lb
ed="T" n="0860a17"/>山</placeName></placeName>，冥心巡<anchor xml:id="beg0860sgsz3"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0860sgsz3"/>。後登<placeName key="PL000000029939">蒼梧</placeName>野，陟<placeName key="PL000000028929">祝融峯</placeName>。然<persName key="A008355">韶<lb
ed="T" n="0860a18"/><roleName>師</roleName></persName>或隨或否。迴于<placeName key="PL000000011455">浙</placeName>，來還棲息<persName key="A008355">韶<roleName>師</roleName></persName>法會。<lb
ed="T" n="0860a19"/>其為人也，稠人廣眾，往往滑稽，有好戲噱<lb
ed="T" n="0860a20"/>者則狎之，膠漆如也。故高達之者，置之於度<lb
ed="T" n="0860a21"/>外矣。唯<persName key="A008355">韶<roleName>師</roleName></persName>默而識之，謂人曰：「<persName key="A013524">蘊<roleName>公</roleName></persName>癡狂，<lb
ed="T" n="0860a22"/><ref type="person" target="#A008355">吾</ref>不測其邊際焉。」因有疾，求僧作懺悔文，<lb
ed="T" n="0860a23"/>誦經及密呪各論幾百藏為度，方知其密<lb
ed="T" n="0860a24"/>持之不懈。嘗謂道友曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A013524">吾</ref>生無益於人，欲<lb
ed="T" n="0860a25"/>投<placeName key="PL000000014554">宴坐峯</placeName>，不然石梁下，所願早預賢聖之<lb
ed="T" n="0860a26"/>儔也。」其道友多沮其計。以<date key="j20766592076688" notAfter-iso="+0973-09-04" notBefore-iso="+0973-08-06"><name>開寶</name>六年七月</date><lb
ed="T" n="0860a27"/>內，無疾坐終，如入禪定。時炎蒸，停屍二<lb
ed="T" n="0860a28"/>七日，身無欹側，竅無氣穢。及遷神座，就<lb
ed="T" n="0860a29"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000014699">寺</ref>之東隅闍維，煨燼中收舍利外，舌根不<pb ed="T" n="0860b" xml:id="T50.2061.0860b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0860b01"/>壞。灰寒拾之，如紅芙蕖色，柔軟可憐。或曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0860b02"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A013524">伊僧</ref>別無奇異，此物偶存。」乃重燔爇其舌，<lb
ed="T" n="0860b03"/>隨同火色，遲久還如蓮葉。遂議結小塔于<lb
ed="T" n="0860b04"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000014699">寺</ref>中緘藏。後有不信者重燒鍛，凡數十過<lb
ed="T" n="0860b05"/>矣。<persName key="A013524">蘊</persName>生不言姓氏年齒，人以貌取之，則年<lb
ed="T" n="0860b06"/>八十餘矣。</p>
